:KitKat::

She just looked at him in disbelief. "I what? whom? ah..How?"
It still hadn't sunk in exactly what this guy was telling her. She 
was nothing special in her mind. She only thought of herself as a 
wolf just making thing happen.  Letting htings just go according to 
the Matrix.  Let the paths lead were they may. That was a general 
philosophy, but not a battle cry. She just looked at him like she had 
gotten slapped in the face.
